        <div class="sticky-note">
          <div class="sn-head"><svg class="ic ic-15"><use href="#ic-pin"/></svg> Private note</div>
          <textarea placeholder="Jots about Marcus \u2014 only you see this\u2026">Priya is the real budget owner. Marcus is the champion. Don't move dates without checking with her first.</textarea>
        </div>
